00:21:20.660 --> 00:21:21.610
[Qué desaliñado.]

00:21:22.220 --> 00:21:23.460
[Mi madre me dijo]

00:21:23.460 --> 00:21:25.290
[que era guapo y valiente.]

00:21:25.740 --> 00:21:26.770
[En realidad,]

00:21:27.020 --> 00:21:28.130
